                <h6 class="bold color-kadin mb-0">Sisterhood Saves Lives</h6>
                <p class="mt-0">The roles assigned to genders for centuries force women to struggle more than men in every aspect of life. Women face similar difficulties, regardless of age, geography or identity, and this creates a solidarity that brings them together and empowers them. </p>
                <p>A promising example of such a solidarity network is being organized in Esenyalı Neighborhood, İstanbul, where mostly worker families live. Working women living in this neighborhood came together to identify their common problems, raise awareness about rights and freedoms and struggle with the difficulties they faced, and they established the Esenyalı Women’s Solidarity Association.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
