            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p class="my-4"><img src="../images/kiz-kardesimle-gucluyum/kiz-kardesimle-gucluyum-6.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt=""></p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12">
                <p>The second component of the project consisted of “I am Producing with My Sister” workshops, which were designed to focus on supporting women physically, psychologically and socially. 300 women attended workshops on breathing, creative drama, rhythm, writing and painting.</p>
                <p>The project was planned to end with an event called “Hand in Hand with My Sister,” which turned into a huge festival organized by all the women in the neighborhood. With its aim to strengthen women’s organizational skills, acting together and solidarity, the festival included all the inhabitants of the neighborhood, including women, men, children and the elderly, and created a breath of hope for everyone.</p>
            </div>

