            <div class="col-12">
                <p>Women of Esenyalı have already initiated a life-saving change by organizing in one of Turkey’s most violent neighborhoods within quick reach of all the women there. This sisterly bond shared by all women in the world is stronger than any challenge they face. The voice of this solidarity, which started from the neighborhoods, will reecho and grow all across Turkey and the world. Because sisterhood saves lives!</p>
